{
  "id": "2020-06-03_screen_english",
  "date": "2020-06-03",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "",
  "movie": "커런트 워 (The Current War)",
  "duration_sec": 768.44,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2020-06-03_screen_english.mp3",
  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.4,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.4,
      "end": 22.0,
      "text": "영화 속 생생한 영어 표현 완전 정보"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.0,
      "end": 24.28,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.28,
      "end": 34.48,
      "text": "6월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 베네딕트 컴버베치와 톰 헐랜드가 펼치는 19세기 가장 센세이셔널한 사건"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.48,
      "end": 36.1,
      "text": "The Current War"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.1,
      "end": 38.48,
      "text": "전류 전쟁 되겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.1,
      "end": 40.24,
      "text": "굿모닝 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.24,
      "end": 41.18,
      "text": "굿모닝 굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.18,
      "end": 43.06,
      "text": "The Current War 함께하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.06,
      "end": 49.32,
      "text": "Yeah. 우리 그 제가 시작할 때 베네딕트 컴버베치와 그리고 톰 헐랜드가 펼친다고 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.62,
      "end": 52.82,
      "text": "You're too focused on Mr. What's his name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.08,
      "end": 54.0,
      "text": "Sorry, sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.1,
      "end": 56.1,
      "text": "We need to talk about Tom Holland."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.28,
      "end": 57.0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.4,
      "end": 58.84,
      "text": "He's the guy I recognized."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.96,
      "end": 60.88,
      "text": "I was watching this movie with my wife."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.98,
      "end": 64.56,
      "text": "And right when he came on the screen, she was like, oh, Spider-Man!"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.64,
      "end": 65.78,
      "text": "맞아요! 저도 그랬어요!"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.9,
      "end": 66.1,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.26,
      "end": 66.56,
      "text": "Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.74,
      "end": 68.4,
      "text": "She recognized him in an instant."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.54,
      "end": 69.1,
      "text": "아, 그러니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.26,
      "end": 69.78,
      "text": "Right away."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.78,
      "end": 78.44,
      "text": "완전 분위기가 다른 모습으로 나오긴 했는데, 이 톰 헐랜드를 보자마자 많은 분들은 Spider-Man을 떠올리실 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.6,
      "end": 82.06,
      "text": "왜냐하면 그가 became a star with the movie Spider-Man, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.24,
      "end": 84.26,
      "text": "Yeah, a huge star with Spider-Man."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.32,
      "end": 84.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.74,
      "end": 89.34,
      "text": "And he plays a very wonderful supporting role in this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.34,
      "end": 90.68,
      "text": "I think he has a beard."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.68,
      "end": 91.48,
      "text": "Oh, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.62,
      "end": 93.26,
      "text": "So I was shocked she could recognize him."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.3,
      "end": 95.48,
      "text": "I didn't even recognize him at first."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.74,
      "end": 98.9,
      "text": "하지만 우리 여자들의 눈썰미는 대단한지라."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.24,
      "end": 101.92,
      "text": "아무리 턱수염이 있어도 한눈에 알아볼 수 있죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.1,
      "end": 102.9,
      "text": "남자랑 달라."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.54,
      "end": 104.28,
      "text": "Yeah, I could."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.5,
      "end": 105.26,
      "text": "Yeah, very incredible."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.64,
      "end": 105.72,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.12,
      "end": 109.64,
      "text": "이 영화 속에서는 에디슨의 비서 역할을 맡았는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.24,
      "end": 113.18,
      "text": "Samuel Insull이라는 사람의 역할을 맡았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.3,
      "end": 115.46,
      "text": "He was known to be a genius in negotiations."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.46,
      "end": 116.68,
      "text": "Oh, negotiations."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.96,
      "end": 117.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.6,
      "end": 117.94,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.16,
      "end": 121.48,
      "text": "That's why he was more pragmatic than Edison."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.72,
      "end": 121.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.36,
      "end": 123.36,
      "text": "Edison is very straightforward."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.92,
      "end": 127.42,
      "text": "And oftentimes, he's not a great negotiator."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.5,
      "end": 128.86,
      "text": "Yeah, and very simultaneous."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.56,
      "end": 129.68,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.2,
      "end": 132.88,
      "text": "굉장히 즉흥적인 그런 성격을 가지고 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.12,
      "end": 133.86,
      "text": "Ah, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.58,
      "end": 136.32,
      "text": "Very 즉흥적인."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.32,
      "end": 138.56,
      "text": "Very 즉흥적인."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.72,
      "end": 139.46,
      "text": "Oh, 좋아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.58,
      "end": 140.3,
      "text": "에듀을 잘해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.3,
      "end": 148.88,
      "text": "And he offered a lot of help to Mr. Edison to support his inventions and to make business deals."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.04,
      "end": 149.26,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.04,
      "end": 155.1,
      "text": "그리고 사회 기반 시설에도 굉장히 영향을 많이 끼친 실존 인물이라고 합니다, 미국의."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.72,
      "end": 157.34,
      "text": "아무튼 대단한 사람이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.9,
      "end": 160.4,
      "text": "But he didn't look like a big character in the movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.4,
      "end": 160.9,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.22,
      "end": 165.18,
      "text": "영화에서는 그렇게 자세히 우리가 들여다볼 수는 없었는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.54,
      "end": 169.58,
      "text": "우리가 이렇게 대화를 하면서 그 외의 정보도 알아볼 수가 있었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.58,
      "end": 177.08,
      "text": "He was in the background, but played a key role in the creation and the spread of electricity."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.42,
      "end": 177.7,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.3,
      "end": 179.9,
      "text": "자, 오늘 내용 기대해 주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.98,
      "end": 184.64,
      "text": "He engineers his own reality, and he looks for needles and hay stacks."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.65,
      "end": 188.19,
      "text": "But how does he know there's a needle in the hay to begin with?"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.29,
      "end": 188.85,
      "text": "He doesn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.05,
      "end": 189.67,
      "text": "Me neither do you."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.67,
      "end": 194.65,
      "text": "But he's so determined not to be the second person to find that he'll go stalk by stalk on it."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.67,
      "end": 195.21,
      "text": "What do you know?"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.84,
      "end": 199.16,
      "text": "이쯤 되면 누가 누구의 목소리인지 모르겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.16,
      "end": 200.14,
      "text": "Who are these guys?"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.22,
      "end": 206.1,
      "text": "바로바로 에디슨의 가장 강력한 라이벌, Mr. Westinghouse."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.34,
      "end": 207.8,
      "text": "Oh, the rival."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.02,
      "end": 208.2,
      "text": "Yeah?"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.3,
      "end": 209.4,
      "text": "The major rival."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.62,
      "end": 209.78,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.28,
      "end": 212.42,
      "text": "What did you think of Mr. Westinghouse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.68,
      "end": 215.48,
      "text": "He has an unusual story name."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.56,
      "end": 215.72,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.1,
      "end": 216.66,
      "text": "Westinghouse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.92,
      "end": 218.96,
      "text": "Yeah, I have not heard that one before."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.96,
      "end": 222.44,
      "text": "Oh, 이게 성씨가 Westinghouse래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.9,
      "end": 223.16,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.52,
      "end": 226.88,
      "text": "But I think he's quite a gentleman."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.3,
      "end": 227.46,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.88,
      "end": 230.78,
      "text": "굉장히 젠틀한 그런 면이 있는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.94,
      "end": 237.7,
      "text": "I thought he was going to be portrayed as a bad guy, like the evil guy who tries to take down Edison."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.7,
      "end": 248.22,
      "text": "But actually, he's also a man of principle and a gentleman, and he's much more business-oriented than Edison and some other people."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.76,
      "end": 249.78,
      "text": "He's very focused."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.82,
      "end": 250.36,
      "text": "He's a businessman."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.6,
      "end": 250.78,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.78,
      "end": 251.32,
      "text": "An entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.68,
      "end": 251.9,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.9,
      "end": 256.3,
      "text": "Oh, 약간 기업가, 사업가적인 성향을 가지고 있긴 했지만,"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.84,
      "end": 259.64,
      "text": "He invited Edison to make friends with each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.0,
      "end": 261.0,
      "text": "Sort of friends."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.78,
      "end": 266.66,
      "text": "He's like, he asked one of his colleagues to introduce him to Edison."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.84,
      "end": 268.68,
      "text": "He's like, 자리 좀 마련해봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.12,
      "end": 270.16,
      "text": "저 Edison 만나고 싶다."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.34,
      "end": 272.34,
      "text": "So please, I need to meet him."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.52,
      "end": 275.54,
      "text": "He's my rival, and I need to know what he's doing."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.54,
      "end": 278.1,
      "text": "얼마나 그, 뭐랄까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.1,
      "end": 283.96,
      "text": "He tried to learn more and more about Edison and his research, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.52,
      "end": 289.28,
      "text": "그와 그리고 그의 연구에 대해서 계속 계속 알려고 하는 그런 자세가,"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.64,
      "end": 291.86,
      "text": "저는 이것도 굉장히 훌륭한 자세라고 생각을 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.04,
      "end": 292.52,
      "text": "Of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.72,
      "end": 295.18,
      "text": "You have to know your enemy to beat your enemy."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.76,
      "end": 296.46,
      "text": "저걸 알아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.64,
      "end": 297.22,
      "text": "이기는 거니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.42,
      "end": 298.02,
      "text": "백전백승."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.5,
      "end": 300.26,
      "text": "He is doing a great job."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.26,
      "end": 303.32,
      "text": "Yeah, 지피지기, 백전백승까지 나왔어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.32,
      "end": 307.58,
      "text": "그런데 초대를 했는데, Edison이 과연 어떻게 했을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.58,
      "end": 308.2,
      "text": "혹시 아세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.64,
      "end": 309.16,
      "text": "Edison?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.77,
      "end": 312.33,
      "text": "거절했죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.65,
      "end": 315.97,
      "text": "I'm sorry, but I'm going to have to turn you down."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.37,
      "end": 317.71,
      "text": "I'm grateful for your offer."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.21,
      "end": 320.89,
      "text": "지난번에 배웠던 표현 그대로 활용하실 수가 있겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.97,
      "end": 322.01,
      "text": "He invites him to dinner."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.19,
      "end": 323.15,
      "text": "A nice dinner."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.29,
      "end": 325.43,
      "text": "And Edison turns him down."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.91,
      "end": 326.55,
      "text": "거절했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.86,
      "end": 329.22,
      "text": "단어들 미리 살펴볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.57,
      "end": 331.09,
      "text": "Engineers."
    },
    {
      "start": 331.09,
      "end": 334.95,
      "text": "Yeah, engineers라고 해서, 딱 듣자마자,"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.05,
      "end": 337.29,
      "text": "어, 엔지니어라고 생각이 드실 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.53,
      "end": 338.21,
      "text": "어, 엔지니어라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.35,
      "end": 343.21,
      "text": "네, 기사, 엔지니어, 수리공, 요렇게 해석하실 수가 있는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.61,
      "end": 345.51,
      "text": "동사로도 이게 사용이 가능합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.83,
      "end": 346.31,
      "text": "Engineer."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.43,
      "end": 349.15,
      "text": "예, 그래서 뭐 수작을 부리다라든지,"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.47,
      "end": 351.47,
      "text": "어떠한 일을 꾀할 때라든지,"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.75,
      "end": 356.75,
      "text": "아니면 제작하다, 조작하다라는 의미로 굉장히 다양하게 동사적으로도 활용이 가능해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.75,
      "end": 360.09,
      "text": "Yes, it's used in a very special way in this conversation."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.09,
      "end": 360.39,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.39,
      "end": 364.79,
      "text": "The most common way is electrical engineer, mechanical engineer."
    },
    {
      "start": 364.79,
      "end": 365.03,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 365.23,
      "end": 366.31,
      "text": "주로 명사로 쓰이는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.45,
      "end": 370.15,
      "text": "이번 대화에서는 특별히 동사로 들으실 수가 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.25,
      "end": 371.95,
      "text": "부정적으로 나옵니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.13,
      "end": 374.95,
      "text": "Needles in haystacks."
    },
    {
      "start": 374.95,
      "end": 377.03,
      "text": "This is a very common expression."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.13,
      "end": 377.91,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.07,
      "end": 380.45,
      "text": "Can you find the needle in the haystack?"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.59,
      "end": 381.41,
      "text": "It's impossible."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.95,
      "end": 382.65,
      "text": "So hard."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.73,
      "end": 383.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 383.21,
      "end": 385.89,
      "text": "Imagine finding a single tiny needle in a haystack."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.01,
      "end": 388.59,
      "text": "어떻게 건초더미에서 바늘을 찾을 수가 있겠어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.99,
      "end": 390.11,
      "text": "해보신 분 계십니까?"
    },
    {
